
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" />
  <title>{{subject}}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f6fa;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #365CCE;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      border-bottom: 5px solid #2f54a2;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .content h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #333333;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #666666;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    ul li {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #333333;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #365CCE;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #2f54a2;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f0f4f8;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666666;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #365CCE;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .social-icons {
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    .social-icons img {
      width: 24px;
      margin: 0 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container"></div>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Cancer AI</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Thank you for joining us!</h2>
      <p>
        Weâ€™re excited to welcome you to Cancer AI, your trusted source for cancer-related information. Our AI is here to answer your questions, provide insights, and guide you through the complexities of cancer care.
      </p>
      <p>
        Here's what you can expect from Cancer AI:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Personalized Answers:</strong> Get accurate responses to your cancer-related questions.</li>
        <li><strong>Latest Research:</strong> Stay informed with the latest findings and treatment options.</li>
        <li><strong>Support Resources:</strong> Access a wealth of information on managing cancer, from prevention to recovery.</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="{{websiteUrl}}" class="button">Ask Your First Question</a>
      <p>Looking forward to helping you,<br />The Cancer AI Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a> or call us at {{phoneNumber}}.</p>
      <div class="social-icons">
        <a href="https://x.com/CancerAITeam"><img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/000000/twitter.png" alt="Twitter"></a>
        <a href="https://web.facebook.com/CancerAITeam"><img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/000000/facebook.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
      </div>
      <p>&copy; 2024 Cancer AI. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>


